item.description:
Come out and support the Demons Aussie Rules Footy Club in their first home games for the year against the Baltimore/Washington Eagles and Ontario.

This will be an exciting day of footy with 3 high quality games with each game being 2x20 min halves.


The tents will be up, the barbie will be firing and refreshments will be available once again so get on down with the chairs and the picnic blanket and cheer on your local footy club!

Post mach function to be held at Tavern on the Water in Charlestown from 7-9, 1 8th Street, Charlestown

group.name: The Boston Expat Aussie Meetup Group
